(1, 1, 8, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><a style=\"color: #0f19c6 !important\" href=\"https://www.health.wa.gov.au/About-us/Policy-frameworks/Public-Health/Mandatory-requirements/Communicable-Disease-Control/Immunisation/Health-Care-Worker-Immunisation-Policy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Immunization-Policy</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">Hepatitis B</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, \'sans-serif\'; color: #0f19c6;\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"https://www.healthywa.wa.gov.au/Articles/F_I/Hepatitis-B\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"color: #0f19c6;\">Hepatitis-B</span></a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l7 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">Completion of the Hepatitis B vaccination series (3 doses) <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">AND</strong> <span style=\"background: white;\">surface antibody level &gt; 10 mIU/mL) </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">Hepatitis B vaccination schedule: </span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">s<span style=\"background: white;\">econd dose 1 month after the first dose, and third dose 6 months after the first dose.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><a style=\"color: #0f19c6 !important\" href=\"https://immunisationhandbook.health.gov.au/resources/tables/table-monovalent-hepatitis-b-vaccines-for-adolescents-and-adults\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">immunization handbook</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">After the completion of the three-dose series, workers are required to undergo a <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">serological test</strong> to confirm immunity (Hepatitis B surface antibody level greater than 10 mIU/mL).</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">&nbsp;</span></span></u></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">In some cases, a <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">booster dose</strong> may be recommended if the immunity levels decrease over time or if the worker does not achieve sufficient antibody levels after the initial series</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">if an applicant receives a Hepatitis B vaccine but does not produce sufficient antibodies (non-convertor), they might not be allowed to work in a role that requires immunity to the virus.</span></strong></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-08 07:48:50', '2025-01-17 08:33:45'),
(2, 1, 9, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Measles, Mumps, Rubella (MMR)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Mandatory for applicants born during or since 1966.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence of two doses of MMR vaccine, administered at least four weeks apart, with both doses given after the individual is 12 months of age.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Serological evidence of immunity</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-08 07:53:44', '2025-01-08 06:53:56'),
(3, 1, 10, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Varicella (Chickenpox)</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l8 level1 lfo3; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence of two doses of varicella-containing vaccine, given at least four weeks apart.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l8 level1 lfo3; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Serological evidence of immunity (positive IgG result)</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l8 level1 lfo3; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Australian Immunisation Register (AIR) history of previous varicella infection</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-08 10:32:29', '2025-01-08 09:39:10'),
(4, 1, 11, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Influenza&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><a style=\"color: #0f19c6 !important\" href=\"https://www.health.wa.gov.au/About-us/Policy-frameworks/Public-Health/Mandatory-requirements/Communicable-Disease-Control/Immunisation/Staff-Member-Influenza-Vaccination-Program-Policy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Influenza Vaccination Program Policy</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #00b0f0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">The influenza vaccine is strongly recommended for all healthcare workers and may be mandatory in certain healthcare settings, such as aged care or high-risk environments.</span></p>\r\nEvidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l6 level1 lfo4; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Proof of vaccination for the current flu season</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-08 10:40:03', '2025-01-17 08:44:51'),
(5, 1, 12, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">COVID-19</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><a style=\"color: #0f19c6 !important\" href=\"https://www.wa.gov.au/government/announcements/mandatory-covid-19-vaccines-western-australian-health-care-workers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">mandatory covid-19 vaccines western australian health care workers</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">The COVID-19 vaccination mandate for healthcare workers in Western Australia, including nurses, was lifted in June 2023. Now, COVID-19 vaccination for healthcare workers is recommended, particularly in high-risk healthcare settings, but is no longer enforced as a state-level requirement. Individual healthcare facilities may still implement their own policies based on risk assessments.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bid