our weeks apart.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Serological evidence of immunity (positive IgG result)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">Australian Immunisation Register (AIR) history of previous varicella infection</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:27:19', '2025-01-10 05:28:44'),
(31, 4, 11, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Influenza </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">The influenza vaccine is strongly recommended for all healthcare workers and may be mandatory in certain healthcare settings, such as aged care or high-risk environments.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Proof of vaccination for the current flu season</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:27:19', '2025-01-10 05:28:44'),
(32, 4, 12, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">COVID-19</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">In <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Queensland</strong>, the COVID-19 vaccination mandate for healthcare workers, including nurses and midwives, was <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">revoked</strong> in September 2022. This means that COVID-19 vaccination is no longer a blanket requirement across all healthcare roles in the state. However, individual healthcare employers, including <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Queensland Health</strong>, may still require workers to stay up to date with their COVID-19 vaccinations as part of their workplace health and safety policies. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">COVID-19 vaccination requirements now largely fall to individual employers, rather than being mandated at the state level.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><a href=\"https://www.tga.gov.au/products/covid-19/covid-19-vaccines/international-covid-19-vaccines-recognised-australia\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">TGA recognised vaccine</span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><a href=\"https://www.tga.gov.au/products/covid-19/covid-19-vaccines/international-covid-19-vaccines-recognised-australia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: blue; background: white;\">https://www.tga.gov.au/products/covid-19/covid-19-vaccines/international-covid-19-vaccines-recognised-australia</span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #00b0f0; background: white;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">COVID-19 Primary dose 1&amp;2 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">COVID-19 Primary dose 1&amp;2 and COVID-19 dose 3/Booster </span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:29:12', '2025-01-10 05:31:06'),
(33, 4, 13, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Diphtheria, Tetanus, Pertussis (dTpa)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Since healthcare workers are required to have protection against all three&mdash;diphtheria, tetanus, and pertussis (dTpa)&mdash;the ADT vaccine alone is not sufficient or acceptable.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Pertussis serology: Serological testing is not considered a reliable or valid method for determining immunity to pertussis.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Proof of a single dose of dTpa vaccine within the last 10 years.</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:29:12', '2025-01-10 05:31:06'),
(34, 4, 14, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">Hepatitis A</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><a style=\"color: #0f19c6 !important\"href=\"https://immunisationhandbook.health.gov.au/contents/vaccine-preventable-diseases/hepatitis-a\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">immunization handbook</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 5.0pt 0in 5.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">In <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Queensland</strong>, the <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Hepatitis A vaccine</strong> is <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">not mandatory</strong> for all healthcare workers, but it is required for specific high-risk roles. These roles include healthcare workers who are working in remote Indigenous communities, with Indigenous children, or in areas where sanitation is a concern.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 5.0pt 0in 5.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">If you are working in these high-risk settings, it is recommended or required to receive the Hepatitis A vaccine. For most other healthcare roles, the vaccine is not mandatory, but it may be recommended depending on the specific risks involved in the workplace​</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence of two doses of vaccine</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Serological evidence of immunity </span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:31:09', '2025-01-17 09:31:16'),
(35, 4, 15, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">Tuberculosis (TB):</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><a href=\"https://www.health.qld.gov.au/clinical-practice/guidelines-procedures/diseases-infection/diseases/tuberculosis/screening/healthcare-workers-students\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: blue; background: white;\">https://www.health.qld.gov.au/clinical-practice/guidelines-procedures/diseases-infection/diseases/tuberculosis/screening/healthcare-workers-students</span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\"><br>TB risk assessment is required for all new clinical healthcare workers, including nurses, to evaluate exposure risks and the need for screening before employment</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Tuberculosis control protocol</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><a href=\"https://www.health.qld.gov.au/system-governance/policies-standards/health-service-directives/tuberculosis-control/tuberculosis-control-protocol\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: blue; background: white;\">https://www.health.qld.gov.au/system-governance/policies-standards/health-service-directives/tuberculosis-control/tuberculosis-control-protocol</span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Proof of a BCG vaccination</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Interferon Gamma Release Assay (IGRA) blood test, such as QuantiFERON-TB Gold</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Mantoux test</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> / T</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">uberculin skin test (TST)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">TB screening</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">questionnaire</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:31:09', '2025-01-10 05:34:23'),
(36, 4, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">Polio</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><a style=\"color: #0f19c6 !important\"href=\"https://immunisationhandbook.health.gov.au/recommendations/healthcare-workers-who-may-have-contact-with-people-with-polio-are-recommended-to-receive-booster-doses-of-ipv-containing-vaccine-every-10-years\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">immunization handbook</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Polio vaccination is generally <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">recommended</strong> but not <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">mandatory</strong> for healthcare workers, including nurses and midwives, across all states. Each state follows the guidelines in the Australian Immunisation Handbook, which recommends a booster dose of the inactivated poliovirus (IPV) every 10 years for healthcare workers who may come into contact with polio.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">These recommendations are based on occupational risk, with no strict statewide mandates for polio vaccination in healthcare settings, but individual facilities may set specific policies for high-risk exposure roles. For more guidance, see the Australian Immunisation Handbook&rsquo;s section on healthcare worker vaccinations.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Proof of receiving the inactivated polio vaccine (IPV)</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">often recorded in (AIR)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Serological evidence of immunity (Antibody Test)</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:34:26', '2025-01-17 09:32:28'),
(37, 5, 8, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><a style=\"color: #0f19c6 !important\"href=\"https://www.sahealth.sa.gov.au/wps/wcm/connect/c5d3b28042de6261b83cfe8cd21c605e/FINAL+-+HCW+Immunisation+FAQs++v1.1+January+2018.pdf?MOD=AJPERES&amp;amp;CACHEID=ROOTWORKSPACE-c5d3b28042de6261b83cfe8cd21c605e-nKOAYw5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Policy-guidance</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">Hepatitis B</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><a href=\"https://www.sahealth.sa.gov.au/wps/wcm/connect/09b7a61c-68e5-4369-9e76-870b92446d17/FACT+SHEET-HepatitisB-YGW-February2016.pdf?MOD=AJPERES\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: blue;\">https://www.sahealth.sa.gov.au/wps/wcm/connect/09b7a61c-68e5-4369-9e76-870b92446d17/FACT+SHEET-HepatitisB-YGW-February2016.pdf?MOD=AJPERES</span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">Completion of the Hepatitis B vaccination series (3 doses) <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">AND</strong> <span style=\"background: white;\">surface antibody level &gt; 10 mIU/mL) </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">Hepatitis B vaccination schedule: </span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">s<span style=\"background: white;\">econd dose 1 month after the first dose, and third dose 6 months after the first dose.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: #0f19c6 !important\" href=\"https://immunisationhandbook.health.gov.au/resources/tables/table-monovalent-hepatitis-b-vaccines-for-adolescents-and-adults\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">immunization handbook</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">After the completion of the three-dose series, workers are required to undergo a <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">serological test</strong> to confirm immunity (Hepatitis B surface antibody level greater than 10 mIU/mL).</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">In some cases, a&nbsp;<strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">booster dose</strong> may be recommended if the immunity levels decrease over time or if the worker does not achieve sufficient antibody levels after the initial series</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">if an applicant receives a Hepatitis B vaccine but does not produce sufficient antibodies (non-convertor), they might not be allowed to work in a role that requires immunity to the virus.</span></strong></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:34:26', '2025-01-17 09:34:31'),
(38, 5, 9, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Measles, Mumps, Rubella (MMR)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Mandatory for applicants born during or since 1966.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence of two doses of MMR vaccine, administered at least four weeks apart, with both doses given after the individual is 12 months of age.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Serological evidence of immunity</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:41:19', '2025-01-10 05:42:40'),
(39, 5, 10, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Varicella (Chickenpox)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #00b0f0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence of two doses of varicella-containing vaccine, given at least four weeks apart.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Serological evidence of immunity (positive IgG result)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Australian Immunisation Register (AIR) history of previous varicella infection</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:41:19', '2025-01-10 05:42:40'),
(40, 5, 11, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Influenza </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">The </span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">influenza vaccine<strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"> is </strong>strongly recommended<strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"> for all healthcare workers and may be </strong>mandatory<strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"> in certain healthcare settings, such as </strong>aged care<strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"> or </strong>high-risk<strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"> environments.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Proof of vaccination for the current flu season</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:42:42', '2025-01-10 05:44:20');
