(68, 8, 12, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">COVID-19</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">In <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Tasmania</strong>, <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">COVID-19 vaccination is no longer mandatory</strong> for all healthcare workers across the state. However, <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">individual employers</strong>, such as hospitals and aged care facilities, may still enforce vaccination policies depending on the risk level and workplace safety protocols. It is <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">strongly recommended</strong> for healthcare workers, particularly in high-risk settings, to stay up to date with COVID-19 vaccinations, including receiving booster doses.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.tga.gov.au/products/covid-19/covid-19-vaccines/international-covid-19-vaccines-recognised-australia\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">TGA recognised vaccine</span></a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #00b0f0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><a href=\"https://www.tga.gov.au/products/covid-19/covid-19-vaccines/international-covid-19-vaccines-recognised-australia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: blue; background: white;\">https://www.tga.gov.au/products/covid-19/covid-19-vaccines/international-covid-19-vaccines-recognised-australia</span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #00b0f0; background: white;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt